Metadata: A non-peroxide norsesterterpen​e from a marine sponge "Hyrtios erecta"

A new norsesterterpen​e, hyrtial 4, and known sesterterpenes, 1-3, have been isolated from an anti-​inflammatory active crude extract of the Tongan black sponge "Hyrtios erecta". This is the first such compound to be reported from the subclass Dictyoceratida.
